ZH: 这家工厂的传送带很长。
EN: The conveyor belt in this factory is very long.

ZH: 请小心不要把手伸到传送带上。
EN: Please be careful not to put your hand on the conveyor belt.

ZH: 传送带上的产品会自动运送到包装区。
EN: The products on the conveyor belt will be automatically transported to the packaging area.

ZH: 工人们将箱子放在传送带上。
EN: The workers put the boxes on the conveyor belt.

ZH: 这台机器的传送带速度很快。
EN: The conveyor belt speed of this machine is very fast.

ZH: 我们需要一个更大的传送带来处理订单的增加。
EN: We need a larger conveyor belt to handle the increase in orders.

ZH: 食品从传送带出来后会被检查。
EN: The food will be inspected after it comes out of the conveyor belt.

ZH: 在装配线上使用传送带可以提高生产效率。
EN: Using a conveyor belt on the assembly line can improve production efficiency.

ZH: 传送带上的物品会直接运送到货车上。
EN: The items on the conveyor belt will be directly transported to the truck.

ZH: 这个仓库使用自动化传送带系统来管理货物。
EN: This warehouse uses an automated conveyor belt system to manage goods.

ZH: 传送带上的包裹会被扫描并分配给相应的区域。
EN: The packages on the conveyor belt will be scanned and assigned to the respective areas.

ZH: 这个工厂为了节约人力，大部分工作都由传送带完成。
EN: In order to save manpower, most of the work in this factory is done by conveyor belts.

ZH: 传送带系统的维护非常重要，以确保其正常运行。
EN: The maintenance of the conveyor belt system is crucial to ensure its proper operation.

ZH: 传送带上掉落的物品需要立即被工人捡起来。
EN: The items that fall off the conveyor belt need to be picked up by the workers immediately.

ZH: 请确保传送带上没有杂物，以免造成故障。
EN: Please make sure there are no foreign objects on the conveyor belt to avoid malfunctions.

ZH: 这个传送带系统可以同时运输多种不同类型的产品。
EN: This conveyor belt system can transport multiple different types of products at the same time.

ZH: 传送带的速度可以根据需要进行调整。
EN: The speed of the conveyor belt can be adjusted according to needs.

ZH: 这个仓库的传送带可以承载重物。
EN: The conveyor belt in this warehouse can carry heavy loads.

ZH: 传送带上的货物需要进行标记以便分辨。
EN: The goods on the conveyor belt need to be labeled for identification.

ZH: 工人们负责监控传送带的运行情况。
EN: The workers are responsible for monitoring the operation of the conveyor belt.
